            With this add-on you will be able to configure <strong>single sign on</strong> for your Bamboo Server.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 10pt;">
            We support all <strong>SAML 2.0 compliant Identity Providers</strong> including ADFS, Azure AD,
            Okta, Google
